content.rendered:
Our partners :
  • Cybelius is a partner with Inetum for the optimised integration of Keenaï SIEM with its products.
  • Cybelius is a distributor and user of the architecture security audit and mapping software of Network Perception.
  • Cybelius is a partner of SEMERU, a company of FAYAT ENERGIE SERVICES, to deliver an integrated Industrial IT and Cybersecurity offer to customers.
  • Cybelius is a partner of Cybelius Services, an integrator in Switzerland.
Become our partner ?

Would you like to participate in our projects? Bring your ideas, your solutions?

Contact us at contact@cybelius.fr
